songs.title: The Incredible True Story (Trailer)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
I am the greatest
I, I, I, I, I (am the greatest)
I am the greatest

[Verse]
Fuck 'em, I will never love 'em, I'm way up
Bitch you know I've been above 'em (the greatest), I stay up

[Transmission: Thomas, Thalia & (Kai)]
Shit never works, how do I turn this thing on?
Cheap shit never works
You have to push the button, Thomas
(Yeah, the one on the top right, where it's always been since the beginning of time, fucking dumbass)
I heard that, bite me Kai
